sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Nguoi dung
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant AU as AuthController
    participant ID as ASP.NET Core Identity
    participant JWT as JWT Generator
    participant MW as JWT Bearer Middleware
    participant PC as Protected Controller

    U->>FE: Dang nhap
    FE->>AU: POST /api/Auth/login
    AU->>ID: Kiem tra email va mat khau

    alt Thong tin dang nhap hop le
        ID-->>AU: Xac thuc thanh cong
        AU->>JWT: Tao token voi NameIdentifier, Email, Role, Jti
        JWT-->>AU: JWT token
        AU-->>FE: 200 OK + token
        FE->>FE: Luu token
        FE->>MW: Request toi API + Authorization Bearer token
        MW->>MW: Kiem tra chu ky, issuer, audience, lifetime
        MW->>MW: OnTokenValidated kiem tra user ton tai va khong bi khoa

        alt Token hop le va user duoc phep
            MW->>PC: Chuyen request vao controller co Authorize
            PC-->>FE: Du lieu hoac ket qua nghiep vu
        else Token het han hoac khong hop le
            MW-->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
        else Tai khoan bi khoa
            MW-->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
        end
    else Sai email hoac mat khau
        ID-->>AU: Xac thuc that bai
        AU-->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
    end
